data.description: Beautiful 2018 new 2,595 sqft Contemporary home with dual masters, 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, that is sited on an escarpment overlooking the historical Cedar Crest Golf Course. Oversized windows in the 21x18 living room showcase the amazing view. The home features 10' ceilings throughout, hardwoods, low e windows. Kitchen with custom ceiling height cabinets, Butler's Pantry, stainless steel appliances, gas range, spacious waterfall quartz countertop island with storage. Beautiful 16x15 second floor master suite has a large shower, soaking tub, Carrara marble, an additional 9x8 sitting area, walk-in closet and incredible views through the oversized windows. fourth bedroom or bonus room upstairs with spacious covered balcony and amazing Eastern views. Minutes to dwtwn Dallas.
